{"tid":1397191,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有啲post重衰過紅媒cctvb， 請注意修辭用字","createTime":"2019-08-02T11:05:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T11:43:53.000Z","uid":276716,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cb875f27e154ea32ccd51485501bbd0d54b75a81","tid":1397191,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T11:05:00.000Z","msg":"出post因爲睇到眼火爆，啲post用字衰過cctvb，自我矮化又有，偏幫軍政府又有，抹黑義士都有，重要過千正評。<br />\n<br />\n❌安家費<br />\n你估義士係黑社會？實畀對家屈義士係收錢做嘢。唔該正名為<span style=\"color: red;\">義助金</span>。<br />\n<br />\n❌沒收/充公/收走物資<br />\n係<span style=\"color: red;\">侵奪/強搶/掠走</span>私人財產呀。唔好將呢種行為合理化。<br />\n<br />\n唔該出post前睇清楚用字，如果分唔到上面用字有咩分別，請唔好用中文出post。拜託<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fee72401d7c5ccfc4e4dc16c34684a43606f5cc2","tid":1397191,"uid":75156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T11:06:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌 我屌過"},{"pid":"aad31c1ac95b83a1d9c4d62ab3d13b9f19b0ec56","tid":1397191,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T11:43:53.000Z","msg":"阿爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n爺佢老母"}]}